task.summary: Pushing all code on Github, initial commit
The workspace list is now filtered on null values first since they exist in the JSON returned by the API. Fixed #1 Also updated the string to version 1.3.2 in the info screen
Changed the onKeyUp method and added override annotation. Deleted a work around since it's fixed in the API. Changed the way the activities close to open the gate keeper
Fixed a null pointer exception with the flow of activity methods
Removed redundant calls for the oath-token
